        "meta_description": "Masterchef judge John Torode 'petrified' his wife Lisa Faulkner when they met on the cooking show back in 2010, but luckily the pair have been in love ever since",
        "meta_lang": "en",
        "meta_favicon": "https://s2-prod.dailystar.co.uk/@trinitymirrordigital/chameleon-branding/publications/dailystar/img/favicon.23503f7410f84687.ico",
